<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <ti      <div class="phase-header"><span class="phase-icon">🍦</span><span class="phase-title">Phase 1: Mobile Ice Cream Vendors</span></div>le>Chimes Commercial Roadmap</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/app.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/strategy-favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #fff0f5 0%, #ffe5d0 100%);
      color: #1a2233;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .roadmap-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6f91 0%, #ffb86c 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 0 0 32px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px #ff6f9122;
    }
    .roadmap-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 0.7rem 0;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .roadmap-hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 600px;
      opacity: 0.97;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 1.5rem auto 2.5rem auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px #ff6f910d;
      padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem 2.5rem 2.5rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .phase-card {
      background: linear-gradient(100deg, #fff0f5 60%, #ffe5d0 100%);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px #ff6f910a;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
      border-left: 6px solid #ff6f91;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .phase-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 6px 32px #ff6f9122;
    }
    .phase-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .phase-icon {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 4px #ff6f9122);
    }
    .phase-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #ff6f91;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .phase-goal {
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      color: #3a4a6a;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .tick-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      font-size: 1.07rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      gap: 0.7em;
    }
    .tick-icon {
      color: #22b573;
      font-size: 1.25em;
      margin-right: 0.5em;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    ul {
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      font-size: 1.04rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container { padding: 1.2rem 0.5rem; }
      .phase-card { padding: 1.2rem 0.7rem 1rem 0.7rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="roadmap-hero" style="position: relative;">
    <a href="/business-strategy.html" style="
      position: absolute;
      left: 1.5rem;
      top: 1.5rem;
      padding: 0.32em 1em;
      background: #f5faff;
      color: #2a7cff;
      border: 1.5px solid #e0e6ed;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #2a7cff0a;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border 0.2s;
      z-index: 2;
    "
    onmouseover="this.style.background='#eaf1fb';this.style.color='#1a5bb8';this.style.borderColor='#2a7cff'"
    onmouseout="this.style.background='#f5faff';this.style.color='#2a7cff';this.style.borderColor='#e0e6ed'"
    >&larr; Back</a>
    <h1>Chimes Commercial Roadmap</h1>
    <p>This roadmap outlines how Chimes will scale, generate revenue, and deliver monetization opportunities for investors and stakeholders.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
  <!-- Phase 4 moved below -->
    <div class="phase-card">
      <div class="phase-header"><span class="phase-icon">�🚦</span><span class="phase-title">Phase 1: Launch & Early Traction</span></div>
      <div class="phase-goal">Goal: Launch with ice cream vendors, prove product-market fit, and establish initial revenue streams.</div>
      <div class="phase-ticks">
        <div class="tick-item"><span class="tick-icon">&#10003;</span> Live commercial trial with ice cream vendors</div>
        <div class="tick-item"><span class="tick-icon">&#10003;</span> 10,000 customer downloads</div>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>Ice cream vendor lead generation and onboarding</li>
        <li>Basic subscription model for vendor features</li>
        <li>Premium customization options (icons, notification tones)</li>
        <li>Vendor-specific Chimes powered apps</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-card">
      <div class="phase-header"><span class="phase-icon">�</span><span class="phase-title">Phase 2: Food Trucks & Pop-up Vendors</span></div>
      <div class="phase-goal">Goal: Expand to food trucks and pop-up vendors, scaling lead generation and revenue diversification.</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Food truck and pop-up vendor lead generation & scaling</li>
        <li>Enhanced premium tier features and vendor profiles</li>
        <li>Advertising & promotional campaign management</li>
        <li>Customer rating and review monetization opportunities</li>
        <li>Targeted notification and promotion services</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-card">
      <div class="phase-header"><span class="phase-icon">🏪</span><span class="phase-title">Phase 3: Restaurants & Cafés</span></div>
      <div class="phase-goal">Goal: Integrate static restaurants and cafés, building a comprehensive food outlet ecosystem.</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Restaurant & café lead generation & scaling</li>
        <li>Comprehensive food outlet database integration</li>
        <li>Static vendor profiles with basic listings (free tier)</li>
        <li>Premium restaurant subscriptions for enhanced features</li>
        <li>Location-based advertising and discovery services</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-card">
      <div class="phase-header"><span class="phase-icon">🚀</span><span class="phase-title">Phase 4: Advanced Platform Monetization</span></div>
      <div class="phase-goal">Goal: Scale and diversify revenue streams across the entire Chimes ecosystem.</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Premium vendor subscriptions for analytics & promotion tools</li>
        <li>Sponsored listings & featured vendor placements</li>
        <li>Loyalty partnerships with brands and vendors</li>
        <li>In-app marketplace for orders, pre-orders, and meal bundles</li>
        <li>Advanced interactive features and community monetization</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
